headline: What to Expect From Interpublic Group's Next Quarterly Earnings Report
summary: Interpublic Group is all set to release its fiscal third-quarter earnings soon, and analysts project a low single-digit profit rise.

headline: 2 Small-Cap Stocks to Research Further and 1 We Question
summary: Small-cap stocks can be incredibly lucrative investments because their lack of analyst coverage leads to frequent mispricings. However, these businesses (and their stock prices) often stay small because their subscale operations make it harder to expand their competitive moats.
